<hr />
<div class="credit otherwise">
<p>This tale was written for <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silber" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1336090); return false;">silber</a></span> as part of the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-4296254/sixth-annual-scp-art-exchange|">2017 SCP Art Exchange</a>. It is a sequel to the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/sigma-psych-eval">Sigma-66 series</a> they were involved in, and reading that first is suggested if you care to.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stallmantic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3472766); return false;">Stallmantic</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;">OthellotheCat</a></span> and <span class="error-inline"><em>9Volt</em> does not match any existing user name</span>.</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
